Classical limit of fermions in phase space, J. Math. Phys. 42, 4020 (2001) {{DOI|10.1063/1.1386411}}在"The Grassmann–Schönberg algebra <math>G_n</math>"一節描述，Schönberg在1956年和1957年出版的論文。}}、{{le|David Hestenes}}（{{le|幾何微積分|geometric calculus}}方面）、[[戴维·玻姆|戴维·玻姆]]和{{le|Basil Hiley}}及同事（{{le|克里福代數的分層|Basil Hiley#Hierarchy of Clifford algebras}}）、Elio Conte等。<ref>{{cite arXiv |last=Conte |first=Elio |eprint=0711.2260 |class=quant-ph |title=A Quantum-Like Interpretation and Solution of Einstein, Podolsky, and Rosen Paradox in Quantum Mechanics |date= 14 Nov 2007 |language = en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last = Conte | first = Elio| title = On some considerations of mathematical physics: May we identify Clifford algebra as a common algebraic structure for classical diffusion and Schrödinger equations? | journal = Adv. Studies Theor. Phys.| volume = 6 | issue = 26 | date = 2012 | pages = 1289–1307 | language = en}}</ref>

===電腦視覺===
{{expert needed|電腦視覺|section = 節}}
[[電腦視覺|電腦視覺]]方面，克里福代數適用於辨認和分類動作。米基·洛迪古斯（Mikel Rodriguez）及合作者<ref name=Rodriguez2008>{{cite conference
 | author = Rodriguez, Mikel
 |author2=Shah, M
 | year = 2008
 | title = Action MACH: A Spatio-Temporal Maximum Average Correlation Height Filter for Action Classification
 | book-title = Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (CVPR)
 | language = en
}}</ref>提出用克里福嵌入，將傳統的最大平均關聯高度濾子（'''M'''aximum '''A'''verage '''C'''orrelation '''H'''eight filter, MACH filter）推廣，套用於影片（3D時空體積）以及向量值數據，例如[[光流法|光流]]。向量值數據需以{{le|克里福分析|Clifford analysis|克里福傅立葉變換}}分析。基於該些向量，能在克里福傅立葉域中，合成出動作濾子，然後用克里福關聯來辨認動作。論文作者用克里福嵌入，分辨出傳統劇情長片和體育廣播的常見動作，以論證其方法有效。

